e.com/artists/beabadoobee">Beabadoobee</a> ，Clairo，Clairo， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/clairo">Clairo</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/enhypen">Enhypen</a>等。</p><p>自从<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">11月透露阵容</a>以来，该节日已经失去了几次预定的行为。本周早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fka-twigs">FKA Twigs</a>告诉球迷<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fka-twigs-drops-out-of-coachella-cancels-more-north-american-dates-following-visa-issues-3852135">，签证发行迫使她取消外表以及北美巡回演出的日期，她“毁了”</a> 。</p><p>同时，在三月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/anitta-pulls-out-of-coachella-2025-due-to-unexpected-personal-reasons-3848253">安妮塔（Anitta）宣布，由于“意外的个人原因”，她将离开自己的老虎机。</a>她补充说：“我希望将来有机会加入大家，并共同分享那个特殊的时刻。”</p><p> Coachella 2024是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2024-line-up-lana-del-rey-tyler-the-creator-doja-cat-no-doubt-3571866">由Lana del Rey，Doja Cat和Tyler（创造者）的头条新闻，还看到了毫无疑问的回归</a>。在此处查看<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/coachella-2024-review-best-acts-3618348">2024年音乐节的整体回顾</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3851846" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3851846" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3851846" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/EdSheerannewsingle-Azizam-news.jpg" alt="埃德·希兰（Ed Sheeran）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/EdSheerannewsingle-Azizam-news.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/EdSheerannewsingle-Azizam-news-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/EdSheerannewsingle-Azizam-news-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/EdSheerannewsingle-Azizam-news-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/EdSheerannewsingle-Azizam-news-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/EdSheerannewsingle-A